thread.title_full: Thread Logic reviewed by Bryce Lee

author: Bryce Lee
title: Bryce Lee
text: Jen has been great to work with. She led me through the process of ordering for the first time. She insured that our order and logo colors were correct before placing our order. We've since then placed 2 more. We enjoyed the selection of apparel and appreciate the name brand items that are available.
